00:18:03,624 --> 00:18:04,792
Bukan apa-apa.

250
00:18:06,585 --> 00:18:08,754
Kita tak tahu
kapan naga itu mengamuk lagi!

251
00:18:09,171 --> 00:18:10,172
Bergegaslah!

252
00:18:13,467 --> 00:18:15,302
Giraud tampak antusias.

253
00:18:16,136 --> 00:18:18,847
Ada apa dengannya?

254
00:18:23,227 --> 00:18:25,938
Granat diisi peledak
dua kali jumlah biasanya.

255
00:18:26,688 --> 00:18:29,650
Seharusnya cukup kuat
saat meledak di dalam tubuhnya.

256
00:18:29,733 --> 00:18:30,818
Kerja bagus.

257
00:18:31,360 --> 00:18:33,070
Kubunuh kau jika gagal.

258
00:18:34,488 --> 00:18:37,074
Lalu kami mengandalkanmu untuk kapal kita.

259
00:18:37,157 --> 00:18:38,283
Serahkan padaku!

260
00:18:38,617 --> 00:18:41,203
Gibbs, persiapan kita hampir beres.

261
00:18:41,286 --> 00:18:42,454
Ayo periksa rencana.

262
00:18:57,010 --> 00:18:58,011
Apa itu?

263
00:18:59,221 --> 00:19:00,556
Itu gyrocopter!

264
00:19:00,681 --> 00:19:01,807
Sangat langka!

265
00:19:01,890 --> 00:19:03,517
Apa dari kapal lain?

266
00:19:10,607 --> 00:19:13,277
Mau apa mereka?

267
00:19:13,694 --> 00:19:14,528
Gawat!

268
00:19:17,197 --> 00:19:20,159
Syukurlah ini tidak hancur dengan kapal!

269
00:19:20,325 --> 00:19:21,160
Ya!

270
00:19:21,493 --> 00:19:23,662
Itu tangkapan kita sejak awal.

271
00:19:23,745 --> 00:19:28,584
Kapten kita gila menyetujui usul mereka!

272
00:19:28,917 --> 00:19:33,172
Ya, kita takkan biarkan mereka
memiliki 300 tong minyak naga kita.

273
00:19:36,675 --> 00:19:38,343
Kita akan bunuh sendiri.

274
00:19:45,809 --> 00:19:46,643
Apa berhasil?

275
00:19:48,270 --> 00:19:49,104
Dasar bodoh!

276
00:19:49,188 --> 00:19:50,147
Apa-apaan mereka?

277
00:19:51,690 --> 00:19:53,108
Naga itu akan menyerang.

278
00:19:53,233 --> 00:19:54,610
Mereka merusak semua.

279
00:20:14,630 --> 00:20:16,214
Astaga!

280
00:20:19,718 --> 00:20:20,844
Mustahil!

281
00:20:34,483 --> 00:20:36,443
Orang-orang bodoh itu terburu-buru!

282
00:20:37,319 --> 00:20:39,529
Beri tahu yang lain kita mulai.

283
00:20:42,699 --> 00:20:43,533
Giraud!

284
00:21:04,096 --> 00:21:05,847
Biarkan aku lewat!

285
00:21:12,187 --> 00:21:13,021
Ia turun!

286
00:21:17,859 --> 00:21:18,694
Ini buruk!

287
00:21:19,528 --> 00:21:21,113
Ini sangat buruk!

288
00:21:31,164 --> 00:21:31,999
Katja!

289
